}# Explore Rwanda Guide

Explore Rwanda Guide is a free, interactive web app showcasing Rwanda’s top tourist destinations, hotels, and local experiences. Works on mobile and desktop browsers.  

## Features
- Volcanoes National Park, Nyungwe Forest, Lake Kivu, Akagera NP, Kigali Genocide Memorial  
- Hotels & lodges information  
- Tour guides and transport services  
- Google Maps links for navigation  
- Mobile-friendly and responsive design

## Usage
1. Open `index.html` in a browser or host with GitHub Pages.  
2. Click buttons to navigate between Destinations and Hotels. # Explore Rwanda Guide

Explore Rwanda Guide is a free, interactive web app showcasing Rwanda’s top tourist destinations, hotels, and local experiences. Works on mobile and desktop browsers.  

## Features
- Volcanoes National Park, Nyungwe Forest, Lake Kivu, Akagera NP, Kigali Genocide Memorial  
- Hotels & lodges information  
- Tour guides and transport services  
- Google Maps links for navigation  
- Mobile-friendly and responsive design

## Usage
1. Open `index.html` in a browser or host with GitHub Pages.  
2. Click buttons to navigate between Destinations and Hotels.  
3. Use "View on Map" links to get directions.                 
